# GitHub Pages configuration for Expressions by Tosha Hanvey

# Site identity
title: Expressions by Tosha Hanvey
description: Original healing art by survivor Tosha Hanvey. Affirmation prints, apparel, mugs and gifts designed to bring calm, hope and encouragement.
url: "https://nathanjhanvey.github.io"
baseurl: "/ExpressionsByTosha"

# Tell GitHub Pages this is a plain HTML site — no Jekyll processing needed
# This prevents GitHub from trying to interpret the HTML as a Jekyll template
exclude:
  - README.md
  - LICENSE

# Encoding
encoding: utf-8
